102
00:06:53,249 --> 00:06:56,999
The critical design principle is
the ACI is not a single AI model.

103
00:06:57,429 --> 00:07:04,469
It is a coordinated multi-agent ecosystem
where each layer handles a distinct

104
00:07:04,469 --> 00:07:06,709
function in the compliance pipeline.

105
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:09,819
The pipelines flows in four stages.

106
00:07:10,419 --> 00:07:14,649
First, the system continuously ingests
the legal text and regulatory updates.

107
00:07:15,199 --> 00:07:20,889
Second, a s-- a legal NLP layer
extracts semantics from that text.

108
00:07:21,789 --> 00:07:27,169
Third, those rules are encoded into
domain-specific language, a DSL, that

109
00:07:27,209 --> 00:07:32,329
capture the logic of the regulation in a
structured technology-independent form.

110
00:07:33,069 --> 00:07:37,919
Fourth, a text code engine
converts those DSL rules into a

111
00:07:37,919 --> 00:07:40,039
production-ready implementation code.

112
00:07:40,539 --> 00:07:44,049
Each agent in the system is
purpose-built for its function.

113
00:07:44,049 --> 00:07:49,399
Each is independently auditable,
and each has defined boundaries for

114
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:51,949
when it escalates to human review.

115
00:07:52,449 --> 00:07:55,919
The reason this multi-agent
design matters is isolation.

116
00:07:56,479 --> 00:08:01,009
If the NLP layer makes a low
confidence interpretation, it escalate.

117
00:08:01,439 --> 00:08:03,329
It doesn't pass a bad rule downstream.

118
00:08:03,339 --> 00:08:06,939
If the code generation layer
produce output that fails

119
00:08:06,939 --> 00:08:09,059
validation, the pipeline stops.

120
00:08:09,629 --> 00:08:12,269
Failures are contained, not cascaded.

121
00:08:13,219 --> 00:08:16,409
This is architect-- this is
architecture pattern I would

122
00:08:16,419 --> 00:08:20,059
encourage everyone building
enterprise AI system to internalize.

123
00:08:20,759 --> 00:08:23,809
Purpose-built agents with
isolated failure models and human

124
00:08:23,809 --> 00:08:25,629
escalation at every decision point

125
00:08:26,129 --> 00:08:31,639
First agent in the pipeline is responsible
for continuous regulatory monitoring.

126
00:08:32,509 --> 00:08:38,379
The layer, this layer watches government
gazettes, official registers, tax

127
