130
00:08:50,139 --> 00:08:56,329
When it detects a change, an amendment,
a repeal, a new enactment, it classifies

131
00:08:56,329 --> 00:09:01,499
the change done by-- change by tax type,
by jurisdiction, and by effective date.

132
00:09:02,249 --> 00:09:07,229
And when it does something traditional
monitoring system cannot, it scores the

133
00:09:07,259 --> 00:09:09,569
confidence of its own interpretation.

134
00:09:10,389 --> 00:09:14,069
Confidence scoring is the
mechanism that keeps human in

135
00:09:14,069 --> 00:09:15,819
the loop for the hard cases.

136
00:09:16,309 --> 00:09:22,019
If the NLP layer reads stature--
statute and produce a high confident

137
00:09:22,079 --> 00:09:27,109
interpretation, say a clear rate change
from eight percent to ten percent with

138
