immediately by monitoring, and

204
00:13:37,230 --> 00:13:38,740
can be rolled back in minutes.

205
00:13:38,890 --> 00:13:42,140
The blast radius of any
mistake is bonded by design.

206
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:46,090
Autonomous compliance does
not mean unchecked automation.

207
00:13:46,810 --> 00:13:48,260
Humans govern policy.

208
00:13:49,210 --> 00:13:53,780
I want to address something directly
that I know is on the mind of every

209
00:13:53,820 --> 00:13:57,110
