226
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:51,140
The philosophy here is
human govern policy.

227
00:14:51,700 --> 00:14:53,560
AI handle implementation.

228
00:14:53,910 --> 00:14:57,410
The system is designed to
escalate, not override human

229
00:14:57,410 --> 00:14:59,740
judgment on high-stake decision.

230
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:05,770
Auditab- auditability is not an optional
feature for enterprise tax sy-systems.

231
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:06,820
It is a regulatory requirement.

232
00:15:06,820 --> 00:15:10,520
Tax authorities don't just want the
right answer, they want to see the

233
00:15:10,530 --> 00:15:12,300
